{"tid":1597902,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[ONE IT]PRODUCE_X101及X1讨論區(129)幾時有新野睇呀呀呀？變哂望仔石喇","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:22:20.000Z","uid":221433,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87ce6ba0a27d1eed8c75ff9ec26bd7e67a4cfd49","tid":1597902,"uid":221433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNZ3nrG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNZ3nrG.png&h=a92187a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>歡迎各位連登製作人<br />\n你可以係度發表有關PRODUCE X 101所有練習生及組合X1既意見<br />\n最重要互相尊重 一齊維持良好和諧既氣氛</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>X1<br />\n엑스원</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">9.02 專輯初動突破50萬張！<br />\n9.15 X1第九個一位粗卡耶！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">FLASH MV</span></strong></span> <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LlQEKB2H7z4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLlQEKB2H7z4&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=81a91dfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LlQEKB2H7z4</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">Fly High ! X1 !</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/4a278ab2c4e91736395425d697c6c7f3/tumblr_pxp96drLwF1yuf0jso1_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F4a278ab2c4e91736395425d697c6c7f3%2Ftumblr_pxp96drLwF1yuf0jso1_540.gif&h=a82d797c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/aa5a31d995499f66a854e8045ad86491/tumblr_pww22o8sAx1yuf0jso4_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Faa5a31d995499f66a854e8045ad86491%2Ftumblr_pww22o8sAx1yuf0jso4_540.gif&h=8af956a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/1670c5986a8a79cdadce9cb980e633de/tumblr_px07jveU3i1xdg2z5o2_540.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F1670c5986a8a79cdadce9cb980e633de%2Ftumblr_px07jveU3i1xdg2z5o2_540.gif&h=e2e4b90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZqHWGh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZqHWGh.png&h=41ebf68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">X1（韓語：엑스원 X Won）是由Mnet選秀節目《PRODUCE X 101》的出道承諾，由最終決選出線的11名成員所組成，於2019年成立的韓國男子音樂組合，成員名單以投票方式決定。成員依排名為金曜漢、金宇碩、韓勝宇、宋亨俊、曹承衍、孫東杓、李翰潔、南道賢、車俊昊、姜敏熙、李垠尚。<br />\n<br />\n2019年整體以SWING娛樂旗下藝人身份出道（各自則有所屬的經紀公司），由SWING娛樂管理團體合約，CJ E&amp;M負責音樂製作，團體活動限定5年，前2.5年為專屬合約，後2.5年可於原公司進行活動。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月27日以首張迷你專輯《飛翔:QUANTUM LEAP》主打曲《FLASH》正式出道，並在首爾高尺天空巨蛋舉辦出道SHOW-CON。官方粉絲名為「ONE IT」(원잇)。<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月22日播放首個團綜《X1 FLASH》。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">要安俊英年早逝？<br />\n唔洗用劍嘅！<br />\n用李鎭赫旋風夠晒威<br />\n赫旋風的確好洗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qxZZe8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qxZZe8.gif&h=0833c36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCr to 藍色女人</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0EtSc2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0EtSc2.gif&h=238a2118&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"136ca2364ecb78279ce138084751716f49780439","tid":1597902,"uid":221433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>X1 엑스원<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/b4af82d475e0ee1c0b69821e2248d5aa/tumblr_puwkxvKtts1qjnqmyo2_500.gif\" da